How to install Glade-Perl application 'print_scale'
--------------------------------------------------------------------

TO INSTALL
----------
There is a standard Makefile.PL to handle some checks and install the package

To install
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    su
    make install (if test was OK)
        
TO BUILD RPMS
-------------
Build the RPMs by calling eg.
    rpm -ta print_scale-0.01.tar.gz


